
=======================================
Run an app image
=======================================

App images dont install the app right out 
They install the .appimage and you have to 
give it permission to be executable. 

$ mkdir application_name

$ cd application_name 

Download appimage, mv to application_name dir

Then in application_name dir 

$ chmod u+x [appimage file]

to change the permissions to be executable. 

Run the app with 

./appname.appimage

or you should be able to click it to launch it if in file exploer

=end=


